ww.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-L%C3%B4i-Ph%C3%A1t/%C3%94-%C3%B4-ca/poem--nkwKog4rhovNtymFbWpRg">Ô ô ca - 烏烏歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-L%C3%B4i-Ph%C3%A1t/author-5J0P_EDGEC1h1gar2eA3WQ">Nhạc Lôi Phát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-b%E1%BA%A3n-b%E1%BB%99-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-Phan-V%E1%BB%8B-Ch%E1%BB%89-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n-h%C6%B0u-tr%C3%AD/poem-Eh4UstTjyO_3CZ7hWLLAyQ">Tiễn bản bộ thượng thư Phan Vị Chỉ đại nhân hưu trí - 餞本部尚書潘渭沚大人休致</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%8Dch-T%E1%BA%AFc/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-qu%E1%BB%91c/poem-UK-2GvtOe_wbSd4b-DuJ7w">Xuất quốc - 出國</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C3%8Dch-T%E1%BA%AFc/author-2WHplYhGibS3kNKVcV5ntg">Trần Ích Tắc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
